    <item>
      <title>土耳其因哈马斯“审查”争端封锁 Instagram</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/turkey-blocks-instagram-claims-hamas-condolences-censored</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的一名高级助手批评社交媒体平台“审查”与哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚之死相关的帖子后，土耳其互联网监管机构封锁了 Instagram 的访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/turkey-blocks-instagram-claims-hamas-condolences-censored</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 05:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊股价下跌，因人工智能支出计划令投资者感到恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/amazon-projects-profit-that-misses-estimates-signaling-ai-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司冒着激怒华尔街的风险，告诉投资者，目前的利润将让位于对人工智能的巨额投资。股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/amazon-projects-profit-that-misses-estimates-signaling-ai-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔股价因前景黯淡而跌至 1982 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/intel-says-revenue-will-fall-short-of-expectations-cuts-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司股价遭遇 40 多年来的最大跌幅，此前该公司发布了严峻的增长预测，并计划裁员 15,000 人，这表明该芯片制造商在人工智能时代的竞争能力不足。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/intel-says-revenue-will-fall-short-of-expectations-cuts-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:07:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
